---
title: Easy Sweet-Chili Turkey and Veggie Stir-Fry with Crispy Shallots
description: Stir-fries are the perfect go-to for a speedy weeknight meal the whole family can enjoy – and this one is no exception! Sticky, savoury soy-sweet chili coats ground turkey and fresh, crisp veggies, with jasmine rice underneath to soak up all that goodness. Lay out all your ingredients before starting to make this meal even more of a breeze!
